➜【八一特辑】军徽永存，警徽闪耀
http://www.sohu.com/a/411077878_100001140	34138
<p class="ql-align-center">在警营中</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">有这样一群人</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">他们脱下军装、穿上警服</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">从国防绿到警察蓝</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">不同的制服 相同的赤诚</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">脱不下的</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">是对祖国的挚爱</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">对人民的深情</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">从保家卫国到守护人民</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">他们以同样的姿态</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">在公安岗位上坚守、奋斗</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">今天</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">我们走进湖南警营</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">一睹警营老兵的风采！</p>
